\begin_inset Formula $l$
\end_inset

 tangent to the conic 
\begin_inset Formula $C$
\end_inset

 satisfies 
\begin_inset Formula $l^{T}C^{*}l=0$
\end_inset

.
 
\begin_inset Formula $C^{*}$
\end_inset

 is the adjoint matrix of 
\begin_inset Formula $C$
