\begin_inset Formula $l_{\infty}$
\end_inset

, which provides the fourth point.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Given line at infinity imaged at 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(l_{1},l_{2},l_{3}\right)^{T}$
