\begin_inset Formula $l$
\end_inset

 back to 
\begin_inset Formula $l_{\infty}=\left(0,0,1\right)^{T}$
\end_inset

 is 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
H=H_{A}\begin{bmatrix}1 & 0 & 0\\
0 & 1 & 0\\
l_{1} & l_{2} & l_{3}
\end{bmatrix}.
\]

\end_inset

Appy this matrix to every imaged point to affinely rectify the image.
\end_layout

